column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, s.specobjid, p.ra,p.dec, s.z as redshift,  p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  g.h_alpha_flux as haflux, g.h_alpha_flux_err as haflerr,  g.nii_#_flux as niiflux, g.nii_#_flux_err as niifluxerr FROM GalSpecLine AS g  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid  JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON p.objid = s.bestobjid WHERE  p.r BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #  AND g.h_alpha_flux > #*g.h_alpha_flux_err  AND g.h_alpha_flux_err > #  AND g.nii_#_flux > #*g.nii_#_flux_err  AND g.nii_#_flux_err > #  AND s.class = &&& AND s.zwarning = #
